<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 100px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888888;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    th, td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 8px;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
    }
    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
    .total {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <!-- <img src="your_logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo"> -->
      <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">Order Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= order.userName %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for placing an order with our learning management system. Your order has been successfully processed and confirmed.</p>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Order Number</th>
          <td><%= order._id %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Order Date</th>
          <td><%= order.date %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <td><%= order.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Price</th>
          <td><%= order.price %>USD</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="total">
          <th>Total</th>
          <td><%= order.price %>USD</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding your order, please feel free to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing our learning management system!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= order.userEmail %>. If you no longer wish to receive such emails, you can unsubscribe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <a href="https://chintamanipala.me" class="button" style="background-color: #4CAF50;">Visit Our Website</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>